# Component Patterns

## Preferred Components

When building UI, use these canonical shared components:

| Need | Use | Path |
|------|-----|------|
| Empty state | `EmptyState` | `src/components/shared/EmptyState.tsx` |
| Stat/KPI card | `KpiCard` | `src/components/dashboard/KpiCard.tsx` |
| Page wrapper | `PageShell` | `src/components/layout/PageShell.tsx` |

These legacy files have been removed:
- `src/components/farmer/EmptyState.tsx` — merged into shared version
- `src/components/shared/StatCard.tsx` — replaced by `KpiCard`
- `src/components/StatsSection.tsx` — unused, deleted

## Toast Import

Always import toast from `@/hooks/use-toast`:

```tsx
import { useToast } from '@/hooks/use-toast';
```

Do NOT import from `@/components/ui/use-toast`.

## shadcn/ui

- NEVER edit files in `src/components/ui/` — these are auto-generated
- Use shadcn components as-is; wrap in shared components for app-specific behavior
- Use `cn()` from `src/lib/utils.ts` for all conditional Tailwind classes

## Data Fetching

- Components should NOT contain data-fetching logic
- All data fetching goes in hooks (`src/hooks/`)
- Pages import hooks; components receive data as props
- Use `useQuery` / `useMutation` from TanStack Query — never `useEffect` + `fetch`

## Null Safety

- `strictNullChecks` is OFF in tsconfig — TypeScript will NOT warn about null access
- Always null-check DB values: `value ?? 'fallback'`
- Known nullable columns: `crops.health_status ?? 'normal'`, `crops.growth_stage ?? 'seedling'`
- Missing null checks cause blank pages (no ErrorBoundary on most routes)
